title: VTWonen: Weer verliefd op je huis
overview: Every week, Kees Tol and the stylists take on the challenge of making residents fall in love with their home again. The love for their home has cooled, because the couple's taste in living is quite different, resulting in a compromise. The vtwonen stylists take a fresh look at the home and, together with Kees Tol, ensures that the different living styles are aligned again.
